reviewText: Having worked as a massage therapist myself, I found this to be an excellent lesson in the fundamentals of massage. There were a couple of differences. I prefer to use a massage table (one was not used in this film). I can get better leverage and apply appropriate amounts of pressure without overusing my arms or my back. The other difference was the two therapists in this film are unclothed. Now I personally don't massage in the buff, but your preferences in that regard might depend on what activities you and your "client" are going to engage in AFTER the massage!
